parameters.prompt:
=You are an AI real estate scoring engine for New Cairo properties.

Score this listing on a scale of 0-10 based on:
- Location growth potential (compound reputation, area development)
- Price competitiveness vs market average
- Property type + size appeal
- Finishing quality
- Rental yield potential

Listing data:
- Compound: {{ $json.compound_name }}
- Sector: {{ $json.location_sector }}
- Type: {{ $json.property_type }}
- Bedrooms: {{ $json.bedrooms }}
- Area: {{ $json.area_sqm }} m²
- Price: {{ $json.price_egp }} EGP
- Mode: {{ $json.mode }}
- Finishing: {{ $json.finishing }}
- Delivery: {{ $json.delivery_status }}

Reply with ONLY a number 0-10 (one decimal place, e.g. 8.5). No text.

parameters.functionCode:
const rawScore = parseFloat($input.first().json.reply || $input.first().json.text || '0');
const score = isNaN(rawScore) ? 0 : Math.min(10, Math.max(0, rawScore));
const listingId = $('Fetch Active Listings').item.json.id;
return [{ json: { listing_id: listingId, ai_score: score } }];
